commentable_entity.title: #men too! Justice for men! DoMENstic Violence!
commentable_entity.description:
Abuse in any shape or form towards any sex is NOT ok! 

Its about time we get justice for the MEN out there who go through and suffer domestic violence in silence. For the MEN who feel too ashamed to stand up and tell their story! 

Following to court proceeding of Johnny Depp v Amber heard, now is the time to do something about mens domestic abuse! 
 #justiceformen #survivor #tellyourstory
